Cheetor/Quickstrike:





Cheetor watched Quickstrike talk to the female scorpion. The Fuzor was still 
dull as a cyber-brick. He ducked his head and tried to quiet a chuckle.

He had to get just a little closer. This was funny. But how did he get back 
on-line? And where did this other scorpion come from? Maybe she was the one 
that brought him on-line, perhaps favoring him over the others peices of 
scrap metal. She must have done a good job of rebuilding him. He looked 
fairly clean. But he still stunk.

A dead branch on the ground got in the way of his paw, he tried to move his 
paw a step forward, but it hit a twig that snapped.

"Oh slag." He knew they had heard it.



Quickstrike turned his head. "Ya hear that?"
